Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:04.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:07.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nwill make tonight sparkle, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:11.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy my somewhat troublesome \Nrival and a black miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:17.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Two steel crows in the night sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:19.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Three more on their other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:23.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Whoa! They've even prepared armored cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kudos to the Metro Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:27.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They're fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:30.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please reconsider, Young Master Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:33.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about tonight's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:37.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you got backed into a corner like \Nlast time and something happened to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:44.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,no apology of mine would suffice for the \Nghost of Toichi-sama, the previous Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:48.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. You're always like this \Nbefore a big job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:50.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:56.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And anyway, tonight I'm not the son of \Nillusionist Toichi Kuroba, your former boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:59.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,nor am I high school student \NYoung Master Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:01.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm the guy \Nwho's got everyone talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:10.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm the I'm the flashy scoundrel.....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.93,0:01:16.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But now that you mention it, \Nthat was a close call, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.99,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,0,,Black Star
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That was too easy! Like \Ntaking candy from a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:52.20,Signs - readability,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief Appears Yet Again \Nand Steals the Treasure with Style!\N\NKid the Phantom Thief Dazzles Police Again\N with His Daring Crime
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:54.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is such a cinch, I could pull off the \Nnext job with both hands tied behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:59.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Number of Kid's female fans skyrocketing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:01.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:05.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Female fans skyrocketing," my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:09.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This girl is no fan of that thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:13.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In fact, when it comes to the scummiest \Nof scumbags, he's at the head of the pack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't let it get to you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:20.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't blame Kid if he gives that \Nthird-rate inspector father of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,a spanking every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:25.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After all, he's... One! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"The Great Thief Who Can't Be Caught!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.24,Signs,,0,0,0,,The Great Thief Who Can't Be Caught!\N\NIn-depth analysis of the mysterious \NKid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:35.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He always either throws away what he \Nsteals or secretly returns it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:37.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's a criminal thrill-seeker \Npretending to be a good guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:41.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what I like about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's cute, like a mischievous boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't let him put one over on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:50.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No matter how you slice it, \Nhe's a criminal! A bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:55.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you saw Kid's next target \Non the news, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:59.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh. You mean the old clock tower \Nin front of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right! That belongs \Nto everyone in this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.18,Signs - readability,,0,0,0,,{\a5\fs16.5}Kid the Phantom Thief's Next Target, \Nthe Clock Tower, Slated for Relocation\N\NMetro Police Enact Strict Security Measures,\N Seal Off Entrance\N\N"I Hope They Protect the Clock Tower," \NSays Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:05.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So don't you think it's terrible \Nthat he means to steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:12.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...that clock tower is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:18.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I heard they're gonna \Nmove the clock tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Make it the symbol of \Nsome amusement park...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Keiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:26.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone's saying that as long as it's \Ngoing away, Kid might as well steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:35.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, I don't know what you're up to, \Nbut I would call off this job if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:39.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I told you before, I'm not Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:45.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"When the bells of the old clock tower \Nring out for the 20,000th time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:48.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,the magus of light will \Ncome flying from the east
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:51.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,to destroy the sinner in white."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that crap supposed to be my fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:05:00.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not a fortune. It's a prophecy \NLucifer the Devil shared with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,L-Luci...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:04.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That clock will strike for the 20,000th time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:07.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,on the night you announced for the theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:11.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Whether or not you believe it is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This goes for the choppers in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:21.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and all the squad cars \Naround the clock tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:25.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Report to me the moment you \Nsee any suspicious characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:31.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,For the guards in each block of the tower, \Nnobody gets past you without my say-so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:35.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But do you really think Kid will \Nshow up, Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:42.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"On Saturday, night of the full moon, \NI shall appear at the stroke of midnight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:46.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}On Saturday, night of the full moon, \NI shall appear at the stroke of midnight \Nto steal the towering clock\N right from under your nose. \N\N- Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:45.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,to steal the towering clock \Nright from under your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:51.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You'd need a crane or something \Nto swipe that huge clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:56.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If he says he's gonna steal somethin', \Nhe's gonna steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the hand of the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:03.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,50 years ago, my father, the mayor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:07.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,spent a fortune to have the hands crafted \Nby a famous clockmaker overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:11.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Several large diamonds are \Ninlaid in the hour hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:14.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,which makes it a valuable piece of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:15.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I imagine he's after those jewels...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's the owner doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:21.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He insisted on checking out \Nthe security measures himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:29.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Protect it from the clutches of the thief \Nwho sent me his prankster advance notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:34.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,saying he would take my beloved clock tower, \Nwhich I inherited when my father passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:37.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right. You can count on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,28 minutes and 30 seconds 'til it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:49.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, Officer Sensui Yoichi \Nfrom Ekoda, 27 and single,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:52.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm going to borrow your name and face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:58.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:01.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What a mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sir! How is it inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:06.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:06.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Perfect. An ant couldn't get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But will it be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:14.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The amusement park side is saying if \Ndismantling it doesn't start tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:17.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,it won't be ready by their opening day,\N so they'll cancel the purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:23.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And if Kid steals the gems from the \Nhour hand and realizes the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shh! Right now, only you and I know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:30.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,that I sold off the diamonds \Nand replaced them with fakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:37.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,With Kid targeting the clock, its value has \Nshot up, making now the best time to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:40.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If they find out the gems aren't real after \Nthe tower's moved, it's not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:43.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But the replicas are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:46.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Even a great, elusive thief \Ncouldn't steal that huge clock
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:50.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,right in front of all these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Stay home, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:59.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Anti-Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aoko, you're the only one \Ncheering against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,By the way, Keiko, have you seen Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:04.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:07.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He said he was going to watch \Na magic show on TV tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:15.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess I {\i1}am{\i0} the only one who remembers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:22.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?! You were out on patrol when you saw \Na suspicious guy who looked like Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:27.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes! He dropped this weird hat and ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:31.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That's Kid's silk hat and cape!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the front entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:35.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,One of our own has found \NKid the Phantom Thief's hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's here, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:48.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes. That helicopter's definitely the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:52.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He gives off strong, clear energy, \Njust like Kuroba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:57.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He also has the cunning of a demon and keen \Neyes that can penetrate a person's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's goin' on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:05.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see an extra helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:07.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Apparently reinforcements from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:10.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for additional help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:12.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the one who found Kid's silk hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I heard the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:16.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just to be safe, please show me \Nyour badge and license.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:17.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:20.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, tell me your name, age, and birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:23.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm Sensui Yoichi, 27 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:24.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My birthday's on June 2nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:29.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori is eagerly \Nawaiting you on the top floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:30.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:34.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Just in case, \Ntell me your license number.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:41.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's 6286-0552-4810.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:49.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's Kid the Phantom Thief! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:57.30,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?! You found Kid in the building?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! Currently, teams \NC and D are in pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure it's the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:06.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After asking his name, age, and birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:11.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I requested his license number as \Nadvised, and got him red-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:13.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,License number?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:17.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right. That thief is a master of disguise,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:21.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so the idea is, it's likely he can remember \Ndetails the average person can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:24.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's what the boy sent \Nfrom HQ as backup said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Boy," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:31.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I repeat! Please seal off all entrances \Nand exits to the clock tower immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:34.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And keep them sealed until I give the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:38.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This way, he's like a rat in a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is Nakamura and Kawata from team D!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:44.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We lost sight of the target \Nnear the third-floor restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:45.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:48.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's probably still very close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:52.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The ventilation opening in the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:54.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Has the cover been unscrewed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It has!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then he's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:06.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please continue your pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:10.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:15.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! The inspector's \Nreally sharp tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unless someone's giving the inspector advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Megure! I figured it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:25.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's the idea of bringing a kid here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:27.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is my operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're in different divisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:34.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. I promised him \Na ride in the helicopter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:37.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and since we were airborne anyway, \Nwe flew over to the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:42.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector! Pardon me, \Nbut we don't have time to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:46.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you want to catch that thief,\N follow my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:47.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:51.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,His identity has been exposed before \Ncommitting the crime, so he's agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:54.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,His plan is starting to go off track.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:57.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the best chance to arrest him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:58.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Who is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Shinichi Kudo , you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:18.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:23.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's a high school detective who's solved \None mysterious murder case after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then you're in a different division, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:28.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with a phantom thief here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:32.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector, a high school student \Nisn't in any division...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:35.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The point is, this is the job of the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,As a civilian, you'd better just \Nsit quietly in that chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid's been spotted in a ventilation \Nshaft, disguised as a cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We're in pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:45.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:49.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is Nakamura! It seems the target means \Nto exit from another ventilation opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:51.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:55.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The prey is as good as in your claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:57.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please tell me your current location.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:02.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Actually, I'm not sure, since I've \Nbeen crawling around in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:06.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We went up one floor, so I can tell you \Nwe're on the 4th floor, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:12.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No worries. All 28 ventilation openings \Nin the building are now secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:16.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Continue support. He's out of places to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:20.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Officers guarding the ventilation openings \Non the 4th floor, prepare to make an arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There you go again, giving orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-This is Nakamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I lost sight of the target \Nat a ventilation shaft exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:28.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's your current location?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:30.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Um, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The east hallway on the 4th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:38.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The target shed his police officer disguise \Nand is currently escaping down the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:40.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Requesting immediate backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-K-Kid the Phantom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:49.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! He panicked and \Nditched his police disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:53.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All officers on the third and fourth \Nfloors, proceed to the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:59.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But how does that boy know so much about \Nthe structure of this clock tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:00.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's no mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:05.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A little while ago, I sent the data \Nwe have here over to his computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:06.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:07.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:09.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:14.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The place is crawling with police officers,\N so taking off his cop disguise
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:18.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,is like a crab that discards its shell, \Nroaming around the ocean floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:28.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It's the time he noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:29.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:42.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector! Smoke is coming \Nout of the scaffolding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-The clock's hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:50.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wow! You're amazing, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:00.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid... Kid, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:06.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's wobbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:11.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What in God's green earth is goin' on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:16.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but can you get us a \Nlittle closer to the clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:22.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:26.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,An officer suddenly came out \Nof the ventilation shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:29.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After nailing us with some weird spray,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:32.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,h-he went outside from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That's crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:37.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then he should be clearly \Nvisible from outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:41.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's me! Nakamori! I found Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:47.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right now, he's—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:54.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Inspector Nakamori, but I don't have time \Nto play games with you guys right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:16:00.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems you've got a sharp joker \Nin your hand this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:04.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But if you're going to call someone \Nhere, please do so only after
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:07.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,cracking the code in the center \Nof the clock face here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,C-Code?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:12.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:13.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The clock face is quivering...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What does this mean, Kudo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:19.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He cut the light that was shining on \Nthe clock face during the smokescreen,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:23.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,then covered the face with a giant \Nscreen he'd prepared beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.51,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next, he projected the image \Nof a clock face without hands
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:31.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,from a projector on the \Nconstruction scaffolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:34.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't a trick like that \Nbe figured out quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.13,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That trick is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:41.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bet he's behind the screen right now, \Nremoving the gems from the hour hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm going to borrow this for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who's shootin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Crap! There's a helicopter this close?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to fly away \Nin my hang glider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:05.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What should I do? What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:13.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, unlucky spirits \Nwandering through Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:19.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Obey the Crimson Covenant. Turn your \Nremains into flames and come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You mustn't, Akako-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:25.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Displaying your power \Nin front of all these people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:32.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Kuroba-kun will...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Kudo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:37.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't hit anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:39.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not the issue...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:42.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And now, the magic show finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:46.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's have a look at the man\N behind the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Who is this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He fell right into the middle \Nof the crowd with that screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:09.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Finding him in the crowd will be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Were you shootin' at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:19.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,By the way, Inspector, \Ndid he say something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:21.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Something about a code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A code?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:26.67,Signs,,0,0,0,,{just katakana syllables, no sense translating}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:30.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:33.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're sure he etched those characters \Ninto the center of the clock face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:35.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In any case, it's important evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:43.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to cancel the clock tower's \Nscheduled move until the code is solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:43.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,{same}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:47.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's what I was gonna do anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:49.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, it worked out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:52.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The clock tower is safe \Nand his crime was foiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:56.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, not quite, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:19:00.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He left a code on the face and entrusted \Nthe clock tower to the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:05.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,taking it out of the hands of the owner,\N who intended to relocate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:08.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,His encoded message is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:08.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,{same; there, already translated}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:15.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Change the katakana to roman characters, \Nmove the vowels over one space clockwise, and:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:18.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,{translated in last line already}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:18.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"The sound of this bell\Ncannot be given to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:22.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \NI haven't heard his name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:24.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's the thief's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:42.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I just moved here today
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:45.50,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and I'm supposed to meet my dad here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:49.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but he's so busy with work that he's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm Kaito Kuroba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:53.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:07.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm Kaito Kuroba. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Like I could forget, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:18.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:22.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your negativity brought it\N all back, Jii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The clock tower job \Nwhen I almost got nabbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:28.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, \Nwhatever happened to that clock tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:30.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You moved, so you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:36.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So they did relocate it, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:36.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:39.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Three...Two...One!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:46.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That ringing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:50.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, the cops investigated, \Nfound out the diamonds were fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:51.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and the city bought the clock\N for a cheap price.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:55.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, time to get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:21:01.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm after a Big Jewel, the Suzuki \Nconglomerate's crown jewel, the Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:05.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young Master, I won't try to stop you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:11.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but like Toichi-sama always said, \N"When you face the audience, it's a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:13.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Never be overconfident \Nor underestimate them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:19.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but see into their hearts, \Nfocus on every nerve in your hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:24.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,exert your talent to the utmost, always \Nmaintaining a smile and elegance..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"And at all times,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:29.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,remember your poker face."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.53,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.97,0:21:43.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, let's meet again under the \Nbeautiful ringing of the bells.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:47.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:23.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know, "Never be overconfident \Nor underestimate them,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:26.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but even though it was just for an instant,\N old man Nakamori saw my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.97,0:23:29.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I obviously need more training!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:32.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks to this, even Aoko suspects me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:35.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,To get through this pinch, I'll have \Nto sew together a time interval,
